32:02.000 --> 32:04.000
Maybe, the enterprise

32:05.000 --> 32:07.000
delivers goods

32:08.000 --> 32:10.000
and gets a so-called goods credit.

32:11.000 --> 32:13.000
This is especially common in trade.

32:14.000 --> 32:16.000
The enterprise tries to get

32:17.000 --> 32:19.000
goods without money,

32:20.000 --> 32:22.000
with a payment deadline,

32:23.000 --> 32:25.000
to return the money after the goods are delivered.

32:26.000 --> 32:28.000
And the producers have more and more

32:29.000 --> 32:31.000
debt.

32:32.000 --> 32:34.000
They need more and more money.

32:35.000 --> 32:37.000
But we have to understand

32:38.000 --> 32:40.000
that no enterprise can give

32:41.000 --> 32:43.000
its goods without getting money.

32:44.000 --> 32:46.000
In any case, it will simply stop

32:47.000 --> 32:49.000
functioning.

32:50.000 --> 32:52.000
So, everything is only to a certain extent.

32:53.000 --> 32:55.000
For this reason,

32:56.000 --> 32:58.000
every enterprise in the country,

32:59.000 --> 33:01.000
as well as in the whole world,

