And in the worst case,

33:50.000 --> 33:52.000
they call in the legal authorities.

33:53.000 --> 33:55.000
They call in arbitration,

33:56.000 --> 33:58.000
which can force the enterprise

33:59.000 --> 34:01.000
to return the money,

34:02.000 --> 34:04.000
