the enterprise loses trust.

35:59.000 --> 36:01.000
It does not want to work with it,

36:02.000 --> 36:04.000
because it misuses

36:05.000 --> 36:07.000
the trust of its partners.

36:08.000 --> 36:10.000
Therefore, the credit debt

36:11.000 --> 36:13.000
