36:14.000 --> 36:16.000
Almost all enterprises have a credit debt.

36:17.000 --> 36:19.000
But it cannot be misused.

36:20.000 --> 36:22.000
And if you have the opportunity,

36:23.000 --> 36:25.000
when you have a financial improvement

36:26.000 --> 36:28.000
of the enterprise's activities,

36:29.000 --> 36:31.000
the credit debt should be returned

36:32.000 --> 36:34.000
at least partially,

36:35.000 --> 36:37.000
at least to your most important business partners.

36:38.000 --> 36:40.000
Then the trust in you will be much higher.

